<section class="l-page-block l-text-block bottom-line">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="de-intro-section col-xl-9 col-12">
                <h1 id="courseHeaderTitle">Degree programmes at INTO Manchester in partnership with Manchester Metropolitan University</h1>
                <div class="courseHeaderOverview">
                    <p>Learning at Manchester Metropolitan University means being immersed in an environment of energy, creativity and diversity. Boasting an impressive network of industry partners, the University’s courses are designed to boost your employability and develop your career, with many offering industry placements and internships.</p>
<p>Among its UK top-ranked subjects according to The Complete University Guide 2020 are: Art and Design (7th), Architecture (11th), Hospitality and Tourism (12th) and Physiotherapy (14th). Though Manchester Metropolitan University ranks within the top 200 young universities worldwide, its design school has a long history as the second oldest in the UK, founded in 1838. Meanwhile its business school is accredited by AMBA and AACSB International, and the Department of Engineering offers accredited degrees in partnership with IET.</p>

                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
        
<section class="l-page-block l-text-block bottom-line">
