<div>
    <div class="direct-entry-intro-text">
        <h2><strong>Highlights and rankings</strong></h2>
        <ul>
<li>Complete an undergraduate degree within just 3 years or a Master’s degree in 1 year.</li>
<li>Benefit from the University’s links with 70 professional bodies and associations.</li>
<li>Many courses include a year-long work placement. Industry partners include the BBC, Walt Disney and IBM.</li>
</ul>

